quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,31,"Wọ́n máa sún Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra mọ́ àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu). Kò sì níí jìnnà (sí wọn)."
  50,32,"Èyí ni ohun tí À ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún gbogbo olùronúpìwàdà, olùṣọ́ (òfin Allāhu)."
  50,33,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá páyà Allāhu ní ìkọ̀kọ̀, tí ó tún dé pẹ̀lú ọkàn tó ṣẹ́rí padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu (nípa ìronúpìwàdà),"
  51,25,"(Rántí) nígbà tí wọ́n wọlé tọ̀ ọ́ wá, wọ́n sì sọ pé: “Àlàáfíà (fún ọ).” Òun náà sọ pé: “Àlàáfíà (fún yín), ẹ̀yin àjòjì ènìyàn.”"
  51,26,"Ó lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀, ó sì dé pẹ̀lú ọmọ màálù tó ní ọ̀rá (tí wọ́n ti yangbẹ)."
  51,27,"Ó gbé e súnmọ́ ọ̀dọ̀ wọn. Ó sì sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ kò níí jẹun ni?”"
  52,16,"Ẹ wọ inú rẹ̀ lọ. Ẹ fara dà á tàbí ẹ kò fara dà á, bákan náà ni fún yín. Ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́ ni A óò fi san yín ní ẹ̀san."
  52,17,"Dájúdájú àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu) máa wà nínú àwọn Ọgbà àti ìdẹ̀ra."
  52,18,"Wọn yóò máa jẹ ìgbádùn pẹ̀lú ohun tí Olúwa wọn fún wọn. Àti pé (Allāhu) yóò ṣọ́ wọn kúrò níbi ìyà iná Jẹhīm."
  53,10,"Allāhu sì fún ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀ ní ìmísí tó fún un."
  53,11,"Ọkàn (Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -) kò parọ́ ohun tó rí."
  53,12,"Ṣé ẹ óò jà á níyàn nípa ohun tó rí ni?"
  54,1,"Àkókò náà súnmọ́. Òṣùpá sì là pẹrẹgẹdẹ (sí méjì).1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ṣẹlẹ̀ ní àsìkò Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - nígbà tí àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ bèèrè fún àmì ìyanu lọ́wọ́ rẹ̀.]
  54,2,"Tí wọ́n bá rí àmì kan, wọ́n máa gbúnrí. Wọn yó sí wí pé: “Idán kan tó máa parẹ́ (ni èyí).”1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn fún “sihrun mustamirr” idán kan tó lágbára (ni èyí).]
  54,3,"Wọ́n pè é ní irọ́. Wọ́n sì tẹ̀lé ìfẹ́-inú wọn. Gbogbo iṣẹ́ ẹ̀dá sì máa jókòó tì í lọ́rùn. 1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn fún “wa kullu ’amrin mustaƙirr” Gbogbo ìṣe ẹ̀dá ló ní ìkángun.]
